---
title: Caribbean Tofu & Creamy Coconut Sauce with Pineapple Slaw & Basmati Rice
description: Give tofu the "Jamaican jerk" treatment and bring the flavours of the Caribbean to your table. For the quintessential experience,
serve the seasoned tofu with basmati rice, pineapple slaw and an easy coconut sauce to drizzle over the top.

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-tofu-creamy-coconut-sauce-b827e543.jpg
